## How to Run

```bash
# Docker (recommended)
docker-compose up --build
docker-compose exec app npx prisma migrate deploy
docker-compose exec app npm run prisma:seed

# Local
npm install
npx prisma generate
npx prisma migrate dev
npm run prisma:seed
npm run start:dev

# Tests
npm run test
```

Swagger UI: `http://localhost:3000/api/docs`
